title: Looking for high elo player with smurf
body: Cant stand solo que... sick of being silver... come help me get to gold before end of season I will gift you skins or RP

replies.body: I dont want your account nor do I need it... the state of the OCE community is a fucking disgrace.. people give up before 10 minutes 70% of the time and have no game awareness its just frustrating
What makes you think high elo is any different?
Give me a good reason why I should and I'll give you this account. I think it's gold something, was plat last season.
